2026-03-02 18:02:06,306 644894 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 2, 'text': '## CSS Class Inventory — sa_jobplan\n\nAll classes below are applied dynamically by sa_jobplan.js or defined in the 3 CSS sources. Every one relates to scheduling block rendering. **None should be stripped during migration.**\n\n### Bar container classes (on `ul.ulbar`)\n| Class | Applied by | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| `ulbar` | JS formatter (cols(), dgrid()) | Base bar container — inline `<li>` list of job operations |\n| `u0`, `u1`, ... `uN` | JS load() `ul.ulbar.u{resi}` | Unit-split: one `<ul>` per resource unit in a day cell |\n| `ultot` | JS dgrid() frozen col formatter | Total header bar in Unplanned column |\n| `unp` | JS dgrid() frozen col formatter | Unplanned operations bar |\n| `single` | CSS only | Single-item bar variant (full width) |\n| `capex` | JS clear()/uldata() `cell.addClass()` | Capacity exceeded border (red) |\n| `capmax` | JS clear()/uldata() `cell.addClass()` | Capacity max border (blueviolet) |\n| `off` | CSS only (commented out bg) | Weekend/off-day indicator |\n\n### Operation item classes (on `li` inside `.ulbar`)\n| Class | Applied by | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| `parop` | JS load() `li.addClass(\'parop\')` | Parent operation (first day of a multi-day op) |\n| `days` | JS load() `li.addClass(\'days\')` | Continuation days of a multi-day operation |\n| `uplan` | JS load() `clsid = \'uplan\'` | Unplanned operation |\n| `active` | JS active() `act.addClass(\'active\')` | Currently active/in-progress job |\n| `slock` | JS load() `clsid += \' slock\'` / menu lock | Schedule-locked operation (corner badge via ::before/::after) |\n| `group` | JS load() `clsid += \' group\'` | Group-scheduled operation (diagonal stripes) |\n| `prio` | JS load() `clsid += \' prio\'` | Has priority ranking |\n| `hover` | JS hover() `addClass(\'hover\')` | Mouse hover highlight across all instances of same WO |\n| `jfocus` | JS hilite() `addClass(\'jfocus\')` | Job highlight/focus from context menu |\n| `focus` | JS load() `$(\'li.parop.focus\')` | Focused parent operation (right border) |\n| `maxrun` | JS maxruns() `el.addClass(\'maxrun\')` | Excessive runtime flagged operation |\n| `over` | CSS only | Vertically offset indicator |\n| `litot` | JS load() `$(\'<li class="litot ...">\')` | Total count header in unplanned column |\n| `bold` | JS load() (on litot) | Bold text |\n| `center` | JS load() (on litot) | Centered text |\n| `whtgry` | JS load() (on litot) | White/gray background |\n| `late` | CSS only (ulbar.css) | Late operation border (red-ish) |\n\n### Color classes (from bhave settings, applied dynamically)\n| Class pattern | Applied by | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| `bg-{color}` (e.g. `bg-grn`, `bg-brn`) | JS bgcolour(), bhave.pln_col/flt_col/unp_col/act_col/max_col/cor_col | Status color background images (traffic light system) |\n| `red`, `ora`, `grn`, `blu`, `gry` | CSS ulbar.css | Status color via background-image PNG |\n\n### Datagrid cell/TD classes\n| Class | Applied by | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| `capoff` | JS uldata() `td.addClass(cls.td)` | Day-off cell background |\n| `capor` | JS uldata() `td.addClass(cls.td)` | Capacity override cell background |\n| `capex` | JS uldata() `cell.addClass(cls.ce)` | Capacity exceeded cell border (red) |\n| `capmax` | JS uldata() `cell.addClass(cls.ce)` | Capacity max cell border (blueviolet) |\n| `capdis` | JS jobshow() `addClass(\'capdis\')` | Capacity disabled (transparent border when filtering) |\n| `cap-off` | CSS only | Alternate day-off cell background |\n| `droppable` | jQuery UI droppable | Drop target cells |\n| `over` | JS ddrop() onDragEnter | Drop target hover highlight |\n\n### Inline style block classes (pug lines 95-152)\n| Class/Selector | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `#priowin .datagrid-row-over` | Priority window row hover style |\n| `a#stats`, `ul#ulstats` | Planner stats tooltip layout |\n| `.ulbar > li.group` | Diagonal white stripe pattern for group-scheduled ops |\n| `.slock`, `.slock::before`, `.slock::after` | Lock badge — corner triangle via CSS pseudo-elements |\n| `ul.ulbar:not(.ultot):not(:empty) + ul.ulbar:not(:empty)` | Separator border between unit bars |\n\n### Image dependencies\n- `red-0.5.png`, `ora-0.5.png`, `grn-0.5.png`, `blu-0.5.png` at `/public/img/`\n- Referenced via `url(\'../img/{color}-0.5.png\')` in ulbar.css — resolves correctly in DUI\n\n### ID selectors used in CSS\n- `#job_planner` — main datagrid container\n- `#jptbar` — toolbar container\n- `#priowin` — priority window\n- `#ulstats` — stats tooltip list\n\n### Verdict\n**100% of style rules relate to scheduling block rendering.** There are zero generic EUI framework styles — everything is specific to the planner visual system. All rules must be preserved during migration.'}
