2026-03-03 07:43:49,396 665862 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 7, 'text': 'APPROACH: Migrate #jptbar to use the DUI datagrid mixin\'s built-in toolbar system. Do NOT just move or rename the div — use the correct architectural pattern.\n\nHOW THE MIXIN TOOLBAR WORKS (datagrid.pug):\n- Line 44: Reads cfg.toolbar as an array from JSON config\n- Line 45-46: Splits into toolbarFields (type:\'field\' → +fitem, left-aligned) and toolbarButtons (→ +button, right-aligned)\n- Line 59: Renders #<dgId>_toolbar as flex row with bg-base-200\n- Line 84-95: CRUD buttons from asdpx string (not needed here)\n- Line 96-97: Custom buttons from JSON via +button()\n- Line 98: `block` — page pug can inject arbitrary extra content\n\nWHAT\'S IN THE TOOLBAR (#jptbar):\nLeft side:\n  - Resource label + #rescbo combobox (easyui-combobox)\n  - Job label + #worcbo combobox (easyui-combobox)\nRight side:\n  - #dg2excel (export link)\n  - #propen (Priorities button, easyui-linkbutton)\n  - #uplan (Unplan button, CONDITIONAL on !planplus)\n  - #jplan (AutoPlan button, easyui-linkbutton)\n  - #apply (Apply button, easyui-linkbutton)\n  - #bak / #fwd (scroll arrows)\n  - #stats (Planner Stats tooltip link)\n\nPROPOSED JSON (datagrid.sa_jobplan_jplandg.json):\nAdd toolbar array with:\n  { "type": "field", "label": "Resource", "id": "rescbo", "name": "rescbo", "editor": { "type": "combobox" } }\n  { "type": "field", "label": "Job", "id": "worcbo", "name": "worcbo", "editor": { "type": "combobox" } }\n  { "id": "propen", "text": "Priorities", "icon": "flag" }\n  { "id": "jplan", "text": "AutoPlan", "icon": "refresh-cw" }\n  { "id": "apply", "text": "Apply", "icon": "check" }\n\nCONDITIONAL/SPECIAL ITEMS via block content in pug:\n  +datagrid#jplandg\n    if(!planplus)\n      +button(\'Unplan\', {id: \'uplan\', icon: \'x\', size: \'xs\', style: \'ghost\'})\n    //- dg2excel, bak/fwd arrows, stats link via block too\n\nENHANCEMENTS LIKELY NEEDED:\n1. The datagrid mixin toolbar may need enhancements to handle the non-standard items (scroll arrows, stats link, conditional buttons). This is the CORRECT approach — enhance the mixin to support these patterns universally rather than hacking around it.\n2. The combobox toolbar fields need to work with the DUI combobox plugin — IDs must match (#rescbo, #worcbo) for JS references.\n3. Separator support between toolbar groups may be needed.\n\nPUG CHANGES:\n- Remove #jptbar div entirely from sa_jobplan.pug\n- Add toolbar config to JSON\n- Use +datagrid block content for conditional/special items\n\nJS CHANGES:\n- Remove .linkbutton() init calls (DUI buttons don\'t need JS init)\n- Keep .combobox({onSelect}) handlers — IDs preserved\n- Wire button clicks via $(\'#propen\').on(\'click\') instead of .linkbutton({onClick})\n\nDELETE: Remove #jptbar CSS from sa_jobplan.css (#jptbar rules at lines 220-225)'}
