2026-03-03 08:33:25,210 665862 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 16, 'text': "KNOWN ISSUES — toolbar buttons not working after step 7 migration.\n\nThe toolbar was migrated from #jptbar (standalone div with EUI linkbuttons) to the datagrid mixin toolbar system. Buttons now render correctly and are visible/enabled, but some may not be wired correctly.\n\nBUTTONS TO CHECK:\n1. Priorities (#propen) — should open #priowin window. JS: `$('#propen').on('click', function(){$('#priowin').window('open')})` — depends on EUI .window() which may not work in DUI\n2. AutoPlan (#jplan) — should call getload('ALL', url). JS: `$('#jplan').on('click', ...)` — verify click fires\n3. Apply (#apply) — should call getload('apply', url). JS: `$('#apply').on('click', ...)` — verify click fires\n4. Unplan (#uplan) — conditional on !planplus. May not be rendered. JS: `$('#uplan').on('click', ...)` — verify element exists\n5. Scroll arrows (#bak, #fwd) — VERIFIED WORKING in step 7\n6. Planner Stats (#stats) — uses .tooltip({onShow}) which is EUI API, likely broken in DUI\n7. Excel export (#dg2excel) — needs investigation, may need DUI wiring\n8. Resource combo (#rescbo) — VERIFIED WORKING (49 options, value ALL)\n9. Job combo (#worcbo) — needs verification\n\nINVESTIGATION APPROACH:\n- Load page in browser\n- Click each button, check console for errors\n- Trace JS click handlers — are they firing?\n- Identify which depend on EUI APIs (.window(), .tooltip(), .linkbutton()) that don't exist in DUI\n- For each broken button: identify the DUI equivalent and fix"}
