2026-03-03 14:47:49,764 807513 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'text': '## Investigation findings\n\n### Formatter flow (WORKS but has a reload bug)\n- JSON config → pug mixin renders `data-formatter="eui.date"` on `<td>` (line 128)\n- `loadData` resolves formatter strings via `resolveFormatter()` (walks window object)\n- Also checks `state._formatters[field]` for function refs registered by page JS\n- **Formatters DO fire automatically on loadData** — both string and function ref types\n\n### BUG: reload wipes page-registered formatters\n- `renderColumns` (called by `reload`) sets `state._formatters = fmtMap` (line 109) — OVERWRITES\n- Page JS registers formatters on `state._formatters` BEFORE load (e.g. sa_jobsched lines 408-419)\n- `load` preserves them, but `reload` destroys them\n- **Fix**: merge instead of overwrite: `state._formatters = $.extend({}, state._formatters, fmtMap)`\n\n### Styler (MISSING — zero support)\n- DUI plugin has NO styler code at all — word "styler" absent from datagrid-plugin.js\n- EUI calls `col.styler(val, row, idx)` per cell, applies returned CSS/class to `<td>`\n- 12+ pages define styler functions: sa_jobsched, sa_jobplan, prodexc, sa_ship, dg_resutil, dg_jobstat, task_todo, gauge_man, coc_man, ci_man, rent_man, logins\n- Pages currently must manually iterate rows after load (fragile, lost on reload)\n\n### Implementation plan\n\n**1. Add `state._stylers` map** (parallel to `state._formatters`)\n- Pages register: `state._stylers[\'priority\'] = function(val,row,idx){ ... }`\n- Also support `data-styler` attribute on `<td>` for string-based resolution\n\n**2. Apply styler in loadData loop** (after formatter, before appending row)\n```\nvar stylerFn = state._stylers && state._stylers[field];\nif (!stylerFn) { resolve from data-styler attr }\nif (stylerFn) {\n  var css = stylerFn.call(el, val, row, i);\n  if (css) {\n    if (typeof css === \'string\') td.style.cssText += css;\n    else { if (css.class) td.className += \' \' + css.class; if (css.style) td.style.cssText += css.style; }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**3. Same styler logic in `updateRow` and `appendRow`** — all three render paths\n\n**4. renderColumns: store styler refs** alongside formatter refs in the map\n\n**5. Pug mixin**: add `data-styler=col.styler` on `<td>` (line 128) for string-based stylers\n\n**6. Fix renderColumns formatter merge**: `$.extend({}, state._formatters, fmtMap)` not `= fmtMap`\n\n### Files to change\n- `public/dui/js/plugins/datagrid-plugin.js` — all changes\n- `html/dui/mixins/datagrid.pug` — add data-styler attribute (line 128)\n- Rebuild plugin bundle after: `bash scripts/build-dui-plugins.sh`'}
