2026-03-03 15:27:54,362 807513 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 1, 'text': "## CSS Class Inventory — sa_jobman\n\n### Source: EUI inline style block (sa_jobman.pug lines 5-96)\n\n#### Tree Decoration Classes (MUST PRESERVE)\n| Class | Purpose | Source |\n|-------|---------|--------|\n| `.tree-title > .ncr` | NCR flag icon (flag_red.png), absolute positioned right of tree node | pug:31-33 |\n| `.tree-title > .ncr.closed` | Closed NCR flag (flag_red_tick.png) | pug:34-36 |\n| `.tree-title span.partid` | Sub-assembly part label, `content:'P/N: '` pseudo-element, italic gray | pug:37-42 |\n| `.tree-title > .opnparts-closed` | Parts complete icon (part_ok.png), absolute positioned | pug:43-48 |\n| `.tree-title > .opnparts` | Open parts icon (part.png), absolute positioned | pug:49-54 |\n\n#### Filter/Search Panel Classes (convert to DUI equivalents)\n| Class | Purpose | Source |\n|-------|---------|--------|\n| `.qbe_job_search` | Body class toggling QBE search mode — hides tree, shows search panel | pug:6-18 |\n| `.jcfpan` | Job class filter panel — margin/padding/width overrides | pug:19-23 |\n| `.jmfilt` | Status filter buttons — inline flex, small text, border-base-300 | pug:24-27 |\n| `.combo-p` | Combobox group panel positioning | pug:28-30 |\n\n#### Framework Overrides (may not need in DUI)\n| Class | Purpose | Source |\n|-------|---------|--------|\n| `#woform div.tabs-header` | Hide outer tab headers (EUI tabs nesting) | pug:55-57 |\n| `.combobox-group` | Blue color for EUI combobox group items | pug:58-60 |\n| `input[numberboxname=DEVIATED_QTY] + .textbox` | Red background for deviated qty field | pug:61-63 |\n\n### Source: EUI JS (sa_jobman.js) — Dynamic Classes\n\n#### Tree Node Decoration (applied by tree formatter, MUST PRESERVE)\n| Class | Purpose | JS Line |\n|-------|---------|---------|\n| `bar` | Progress bar div on SEQ nodes | 1030 |\n| `bar grn` | Green progress bar (complete) | 1031 |\n| `opnparts-closed` | Parts complete indicator span | 1036 |\n| `opnparts` | Open parts indicator span | 1037 |\n| `ncr` | NCR flag span | 1043 |\n| `ncr closed` | Closed NCR flag span | 1043 |\n| `partid` | Sub-assembly part number span | 618 |\n| `bas` | Tree iconCls for BAS (base assembly) nodes | 181 |\n| `seq-U` | Tree iconCls for SEQ (unstarted) nodes | 530 |\n\n#### UI State Classes (DUI equivalents exist)\n| Class | Purpose | JS Line |\n|-------|---------|---------|\n| `qbe_job_search` | Body class toggle for search mode | 92 |\n| `opaque` / `fadein` | Loading transition classes | 662, 1010 |\n| `l-btn-selected` | EUI linkbutton selected detection | 402 |\n| `changed` | Form field change tracking | 797 |\n| `lock` | Tab locking | 562 |\n\n### Classification Summary\n- **PRESERVE as-is**: All tree decoration classes (ncr, partid, opnparts, bar) — these are functional, not cosmetic\n- **Convert to DUI**: Filter panel classes (qbe_job_search, jcfpan, jmfilt) — use DUI layout/toolbar patterns\n- **Drop**: EUI framework overrides (tabs-header hide, combobox-group color) — DUI components handle differently\n- **Images needed**: flag_red.png, flag_red_tick.png, part_ok.png, part.png — check if exist in public/"}
2026-03-03 15:28:25,923 807513 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 1, 'id': 596, 'text': "## CSS Class Inventory — sa_jobman\n\n### Source: EUI inline style block (sa_jobman.pug lines 5-96)\n\n#### Tree Decoration Classes (MUST PRESERVE)\n| Class | Purpose | Source |\n|-------|---------|--------|\n| `.tree-title > .ncr` | NCR flag icon (flag_red.png), absolute positioned right of tree node | pug:31-33 |\n| `.tree-title > .ncr.closed` | Closed NCR flag (flag_red_tick.png) | pug:34-36 |\n| `.tree-title span.partid` | Sub-assembly part label, `content:'P/N: '` pseudo-element, italic gray | pug:37-42 |\n| `.tree-title > .opnparts-closed` | Parts complete icon (part_ok.png), absolute positioned | pug:43-48 |\n| `.tree-title > .opnparts` | Open parts icon (part.png), absolute positioned | pug:49-54 |\n\n#### Filter/Search Panel Classes (convert to DUI equivalents)\n| Class | Purpose |\n|-------|---------|\n| `.qbe_job_search` | Body class toggling QBE search mode — hides tree, shows search panel |\n| `.jcfpan` | Job class filter panel — margin/padding/width overrides |\n| `.jmfilt` | Status filter buttons — inline flex, small text |\n| `.combo-p` | Combobox group panel positioning |\n\n#### Framework Overrides (DROP — DUI handles differently)\n| Class | Purpose |\n|-------|---------|\n| `#woform div.tabs-header` | Hide outer tab headers (EUI nesting workaround) |\n| `.combobox-group` | Blue color for EUI combobox groups |\n| `input[numberboxname=DEVIATED_QTY] + .textbox` | Red bg for deviated qty |\n\n### Dynamic JS Classes\n\n#### Tree Node Decoration (MUST PRESERVE — applied by tree formatter)\n- `bar`, `bar grn` — progress bars on SEQ nodes\n- `opnparts-closed`, `opnparts` — parts indicator spans\n- `ncr`, `ncr closed` — NCR flag spans\n- `partid` — sub-assembly part number span\n- `bas`, `seq-U` — tree iconCls\n\n#### UI State (DUI equivalents exist)\n- `qbe_job_search`, `opaque`/`fadein`, `l-btn-selected`, `changed`, `lock`\n\n### Image Assets (all confirmed in public/icons/)\n- `/icons/flag_red.png` — NCR open\n- `/icons/flag_red_tick.png` — NCR closed\n- `/icons/part_ok.png` — parts complete\n- `/icons/part.png` — parts open\n\n### Shared CSS\n- `ulbar.css` already exists in DUI (`html/dui/mod/vwltsa/css/ulbar.css`) — theme-converted\n- `.bar` class (width:100%) defined in ulbar.css line 2 — used by tree progress bars\n- `sa_jobplan.css` also exists in DUI — may share some tree styles\n\n### DUI CSS File Plan (Step 2)\nCreate `html/dui/mod/vwltsa/css/sa_jobman.css` containing:\n1. Tree decoration rules (ncr, partid, opnparts, bar) — convert image paths to absolute `/icons/`\n2. Filter panel rules (qbe_job_search, jcfpan, jmfilt) — convert to DUI theme variables\n3. DEVIATED_QTY red background — adapt selector for DUI input structure\n4. Include via pug: `style: include css/sa_jobman.css`"}
