2026-03-03 18:06:32,215 807513 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_new args={'title': 'Add formatter support + CSS-class iconCls to createNodeEl', 'description': "tree-plugin.js createNodeEl() never calls opts.formatter(node) — it uses textContent = nodeData.text directly. Also iconCls only supports Lucide icons via $.dui.icon(), not CSS-class-based icons like EUI's seq-U, bas, sub.\n\nChanges needed:\n1. Call opts.formatter(storedData) and use innerHTML when result contains HTML\n2. Add span.tree-icon with iconCls as CSS class (for EUI-style background-image icons)\n3. Add tree-title alias class to tree-text spans (so EUI CSS selectors work)\n4. Rebuild plugins bundle\n5. Test on sa_jobman page"}
