2026-03-03 18:39:12,120 807513 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 7, 'text': '## Tab Structure — EUI vs DUI\n\n### EUI behavior (correct)\n- **Single flat tab bar** with 8 tabs: Main, Dates, Costing, Engineering, Attachments, User Fields, Specs, Quality\n- These tabs are always at the same level — no nesting\n- "Sub Assembly" and "Operation" are NOT tabs — they are **separate include panels** (`wo_bas_inc`, `wo_sub_inc`, `wo_seq_inc`)\n- The **tree click drives which panel is visible**:\n  - Click BAS (root) node → shows `wo_bas_inc` (the 8-tab Master form)\n  - Click SUB node → shows `wo_sub_inc` (Sub Assembly form with its own fields)\n  - Click SEQ node → shows `wo_seq_inc` (Operation form with its own sub-tabs)\n- The outer `#woform` tabs header is **hidden** in EUI (`#woform > div.tabs-header { display:none }`)\n- Tab switching between BAS/SUB/SEQ is done programmatically via JS on tree node click\n\n### DUI current (wrong)\n- **3 outer tabs**: Master, Sub Assembly, Operation — all visible in tab bar\n- 8 inner sub-tabs nested under "Master"\n- User can click "Sub Assembly" or "Operation" tabs directly — this is wrong\n- The "Master" wrapper tab doesn\'t exist in EUI\n\n### What needs to change\n1. Remove the visible outer tab bar (Master / Sub Assembly / Operation)\n2. All 3 include panels should be **stacked or switched by JS**, not user-clickable tabs\n3. The 8 content tabs (Main, Dates, etc.) should be the only visible tab bar\n4. Tree node click JS (`pg.treeclick`) must switch between BAS/SUB/SEQ panels programmatically\n5. Reference: EUI JS hides outer tabs header and uses `$(\'#woform\').tabs(\'select\', index)` on tree click\n\n### Files involved\n- `html/dui/mod/vwltsa/sa_jobman.pug` — restructure the east panel (remove outer tabs, use hidden panels)\n- `html/dui/mod/vwltsa/js/sa_jobman.js` — tree click handler already exists, may need adjustment\n- `html/dui/mod/vwltsa/wo_bas_inc.pug` — the 8-tab Master form (already migrated)\n- `html/dui/mod/vwltsa/wo_sub_inc.pug` — Sub Assembly form\n- `html/dui/mod/vwltsa/wo_seq_inc.pug` — Operation form'}
